# Git Ignore for Academic Risk Analysis System

# --- Dependencies ---
**/node_modules/
**/.pnp
**.pnp.*
**/.yarn/*
!**/.yarn/patches
!**/.yarn/plugins
!**/.yarn/releases
!**/.yarn/versions

# --- Build Artifacts ---
# Frontend (Next.js)
client/.next/
client/out/
client/build/
client/*.tsbuildinfo
client/next-env.d.ts

# Backend (Maven)
backend/target/
backend/*.class
**/*.log

# --- IDE & System ---
.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml
.project
.classpath
.settings/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Security & Environment ---
.env*
*.pem

# --- Misc ---
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
client/.vercel
